{"tid":1116271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"三個女仔揀一個","createTime":"2019-04-19T21:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T08:08:15.000Z","uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe467df43877e5d3f506ae6b4ddd60ea5536871","tid":1116271,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T21:53:46.000Z","msg":"如果俾你哋揀你會揀邊個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本姐姐</strong><br />\n大兩年，對任何人都好好，賢良淑德。識煮飯。一米六幾，微肥同埋個樣唔係太好。不過long D，可能每年見得一兩次<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港姐姐</strong><br />\n大三年，好好傾，好有姐姐嘅味道，有獨立經濟能力。米七，身材中等，面上邊有暗瘡同哨牙。不過long D可能每年見得三四次<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大陸妹妹</strong><br />\n細三年，識聽同講廣東話，身材好好，米六幾<br />\n住得近可以晚晚屌。不過唔係太靚同性格港女，中意買衫同追星"},{"pid":"b657bdf1b7afac34e66d4b704719d25738e01adb","tid":1116271,"uid":181651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:03:45.000Z","msg":"香港姐姐"},{"pid":"ec5dbb45d2235b163fdd67c34952c0cbda6687e0","tid":1116271,"uid":231342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b657bdf1b7afac34e66d4b704719d25738e01adb","tid":1116271,"uid":181651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:03:45.000Z","msg":"香港姐姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:05:13.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4897a7148853c1619bcd87071dac608524f2eb","tid":1116271,"uid":160174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:05:59.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5c932f951081789f4fd753bca1fecc65e53c1c","tid":1116271,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"da4897a7148853c1619bcd87071dac608524f2eb","tid":1116271,"uid":160174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:05:59.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T22:09:19.000Z","msg":"依家就係一拖